sql: SELECT DISTINCT SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR FROM SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER INNER JOIN COURSE AS COURSEalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias0.NAME LIKE "Introduction to Operating Systems" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER > 2070 ;
